# Database Configuration
# ATLAS_DB_TOKEN: MongoDB Atlas connection string/token for database access

# Application Security
# SECRET: Secret key for session management and encryption

# Cloud Storage Configuration (Cloudinary)
# CLOUD_NAME: Cloudinary account name for image/media hosting
# CLOUD_API_KEY: Cloudinary API key for authentication
# CLOUD_API_SECRET: Cloudinary API secret for secure requests

# Server Configuration
# PORT: Port number on which the application will run (e.g., 3000, 5000)

# Email Service Configuration
# MAIL_HOST: SMTP server host for sending emails
# MAIL_USER: Email account username/address for authentication
# MAIL_PASS: Email account password for authentication
# ADMIN_EMAIL: Administrator email address for notifications and alerts
